msgid "Choose your self-hosting mode"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:6
msgid ""
"You can host yourself at home (on a small computer), or on a remote server. "
"Each solution has their pros and cons:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "At home, for instance on an ARM board or an old computer"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:10
msgid ""
"You can host yourself at home with an ARM board or a re-purposed regular "
"computer, connected to your home router/box."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:13
msgid ""
"**Pros**: you will have physical control of the machine and only need to buy "
"the hardware;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:13
msgid ""
"**Cons**: you will have to [manually configure your internet box](/admin/"
"get_started/post_install/port_forwarding) and [might be limited by your ISP]"
"(/admin/get_started/providers/isp/)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "At home, behind a VPN"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:17
msgid ""
"A VPN is an encrypted tunnel between two machines. In practice, it makes it "
"\"as if\" you were directly, locally, connected to your server machine, but "
"actually from somewhere else on the Internet. This allows you to still host "
"yourself at home, while bypassing possible limitations of your ISP. See also "
"[the Internet Cube project](https://internetcu.be/) and [the FFDN](https://"
"www.ffdn.org/)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:20
msgid ""
"**Pros**: you will have physical control of the machine, and the VPN hides "
"your traffic from your ISP and allows you to bypass its limitations;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:20
msgid "**Cons**: you will have to pay a monthly subscription for the VPN."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "On a remote server (VPS or dedicated server)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:24
msgid ""
"You can rent a virtual private server or a dedicated machine from "
"[associative](https://db.ffdn.org/) or [commercial](/admin/get_started/"
"providers/servers) \"Cloud\" providers."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:27
msgid "**Pros**: your server and its internet connectivity will be fast;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: docs/admin/05.get_started/05.methods.mdx:27
msgid ""
"**Cons**: you will have to pay a monthly subscription and won't have "
"physical control of your server."
msgstr ""

